        "comment": {
          "commentType": "SUBUNIT",
          "texts": [
            {
              "value": "Heterotetramer composed of a homodimer of the large subunit (R1) and a homodimer of the small subunit (R2). Larger multisubunit protein complex are also active, composed of (R1)n(R2)n"
